#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:1
msgid "Filesystem API"
msgstr "API de sistema de archivos"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:3
msgid "Filesystem helpers are available under `ptool.fs` and `p.fs`."
msgstr ""
"Las utilidades de sistema de archivos están disponibles bajo `ptool.fs` y "
"`p.fs`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:5
msgid "ptool.fs.read"
msgstr "ptool.fs.read"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introducido."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.fs.read(path)` reads a file as raw bytes and returns a Lua string."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.fs.read(path)` lee un archivo como bytes sin procesar y devuelve una "
"cadena Lua."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:11
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:11"
msgid "`path` (string, required): The file path."
msgstr "`path` (string, obligatorio): La ruta del archivo."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:12
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:12"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "Devuelve: `string`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:14"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Notas:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:16
msgid ""
"The returned Lua string contains the file bytes exactly as stored on disk."
msgstr ""
"La cadena Lua devuelta contiene exactamente los bytes almacenados en disco."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:17
msgid ""
"Text files continue to work as before, but binary files are also supported."
msgstr ""
"Los archivos de texto siguen funcionando como antes, y ahora también se "
"admiten archivos binarios."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:19
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:19"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Ejemplo:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:29
msgid "ptool.fs.write"
msgstr "ptool.fs.write"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:31
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:31"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introducido."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:33
msgid ""
"`ptool.fs.write(path, content)` writes a Lua string to a file as raw bytes, "
"overwriting existing contents."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.fs.write(path, content)` escribe una cadena Lua en un archivo como "
"bytes sin procesar, sobrescribiendo el contenido existente."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:36
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:36"
msgid "`path` (string, required): The file path."
msgstr "`path` (string, obligatorio): La ruta del archivo."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:37
msgid "`content` (string, required): The content to write."
msgstr "`content` (string, obligatorio): El contenido que se va a escribir."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:39
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:39"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Notas:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:41
msgid "`content` is written byte-for-byte."
msgstr "`content` se escribe byte por byte."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:42
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:42"
msgid "Embedded NUL bytes and non-UTF-8 bytes are preserved."
msgstr "Los bytes NUL embebidos y los bytes no UTF-8 se conservan."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:44
